%h1#object-checkout-payment CheckoutPayment

:markdown
  Pair of amount the customer paid, and method the payment maid with.

%h2#object-checkout-payment-fields Fields

.row
  .span6
    %dl
      %dt= field "id", :readonly, :immutable
      %dd ID of the object
      %dt= "payment_type_id"
      %dd ID of <code>PaymentType</code>
      %dt= "amount"
      %dd An string which represents the amount customer paid
      %dt= field "guid", :immutable
      %dd UUID like sequence

  .span6
    %pre
      = preserve do
        :escaped
          {
            "id": 1,
            "payment_type_id": 1,
            "amount": "5000.0",
            "guid" : $UUID-like-sequence
          }

%h3 Notes

:markdown
  Make sure `amount` value is a string.
